thread.title: Killer storm clears, leaving behind floods and outages

title: Killer storm clears, leaving behind floods and outages
text:
Killer storm clears, leaving behind floods and outages Saturday, March 03, 2018 - 01:36 
As the powerful northeastern storm clears on Saturday, it leaves behind a trail of damaged homes, flooded streets and downed power lines. At least seven people were killed by the nor'easter that started on Thursday.
